        #### Installation
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] pip install popd
        ```
        
        #### Functions
        function|`__doc__`
        -|-
        `popd.popd(func)` |`@popd` decorator. restore previous current directory
        
        #### Examples
        ```python
        import popd
        
        @popd.popd
        def func():
            os.chdir('/tmp')
            print(os.getcwd())
        ```
        
        ```python
        >>> os.getcwd()
        '/Users/username'
        >>> func()
        '/tmp'
        >>> os.getcwd()
        '/Users/username'
        ```
        
